<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大地在晃动，阿拉丁开始逃命！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“站住！”马格里布大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抓住了阿拉丁的衣领子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他举起手打了阿拉丁一耳光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的帽子飞走了，他牙齿相撞的咯咯的声音在他脑海中回响着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他摔倒在地上，因为疼痛和害怕哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伯父！”他大声说，“我做错了什么？你为什么打我？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61974</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，我看到你害怕的样子，就生气。”马格里布说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是你的伯父，你必须永远服从我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你不能感到害怕。你不能逃跑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布重新给阿拉丁把帽子戴在头上，擦掉了他新衣服上的灰尘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会变勇敢的，伯父。”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冷静点儿，孩子。”马格里布说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“过来看看我的魔法是怎么把大地劈开的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“魔法？”阿拉丁深呼吸了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布伸出手臂指着地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大地裂开的地方，阿拉丁看到了一块很厚的大理石，上面有一个很大的铜环。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？”阿拉丁问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一扇特别的门。”魔法师回答说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“仔细听好，按照我说的做，你会变得比任何国王都强壮和富有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“告诉我应该怎么做！”阿拉丁大声说，“我什么都听你的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这个大理石门的下面是一个宝物。”马格里布说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是只给你一个人的。只有你可以拥有它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怎么拿到这个宝物呢？”阿拉丁问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抓住那个铜环然后往上拉那块石头。”魔法师说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”阿拉丁很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看大理石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，伯父。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个东西太大了——它一定很重。我不够强壮，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我一个人不能把它拉起来。你一定要帮助我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能帮你。”马格里布说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“除了你之外没有人有力量把它拉起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除了你之外没有人能碰它！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，伯父！”阿拉丁喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伸出你的手，抓住那个环，然后往上拉。”马格里布命令道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后说出你的名字，命令那块石头升起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它会听你的。我保证它不会很重。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是怎么会这样呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“打开那扇门。”马格里布说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁犹豫地看着大理石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我做不到。”他对自己说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“打开那扇门！”马格里布大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁轻轻地重复着那个命令。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的名字是阿拉丁。”他说，“我命令你升起来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他大声地重复了一遍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的名字是阿拉丁。我命令你升起来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快去，孩子。”马格里布低声催促。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁摩擦了一下双手，做了一次深呼吸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他伸出手，抓住铜环，然后往上拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的名字是阿拉丁！”他大声说，“我命令你升起来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁把石头拉起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在那个时候，他移开了门，把它扔到了一边！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到大理石所在的地方有一个很深很黑的洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布探身看了看洞的入口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看到一个很陡的石梯，看不到尽头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁看着马格里布。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“宝物在哪里？”他问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就在这个下面。”魔法师说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们走吧！”阿拉丁大声说，“我们现在就去拿吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“除了你之外没有人能进入那里面，”马格里布说，“你必须一个人去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>